Package main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIA
    The main class for the algorithm.
    Debugging
    Will print out Debugging information if DEBUG is set to true in AIA.
    Node
    Each Node has:
    the elements to operate a binomial distribution a list of all of its children Nodes a score given to it by the process used for Q learning a policy given to it from Q learning of the scores to every other Node a unique state given to it by the process a unique long Id
    Nodes
    Holds all Nodes in the application, and can create, get, and work with all of them.
    QLearning
